= Product Catalog (Physical Products)

== Featured Products

=== Bánh Mì Sài Gòn (Saigon Baguette)
*Price*: £9 per loaf | *Promotion*: Buy 10 get 1 free

The flagship product of Bonu. Traditional Saigon baguettes pre-baked to 70%, allowing customers to finish baking at home for maximum freshness and crispy texture.

*Key Features*:
- 70% pre-baked for optimal freshness
- All fillings separately packed in glass containers
- Includes: pork liver pate, cold cuts, pork floss, pickled vegetables, Vietnamese ham, butter sauce
- Complete preparation instructions included
- Suitable for freezing

*Packaging*: Premium glass containers ensure hygiene and quality preservation.

=== Bò Viên (Beef Balls)
*Price*: £15 per 500g

Homemade beef balls crafted entirely in-house following traditional procedures. No preservatives, making them ideal for families with children.

*Key Features*:
- 100% fresh beef
- Bouncy, authentic texture
- No preservatives or artificial ingredients
- Versatile - perfect for pho, hu tieu, or hot pot
- Family-friendly

== Product-Workshop Synergy

The workshop ecosystem and physical products complement each other:

*Products Drive Workshop Interest*:
- Customers who love bánh mì → attend Bánh Mì Mastery workshop
- Learn to make their own
- Become brand ambassadors

*Workshops Drive Product Sales*:
- Workshop attendees try samples
- Experience quality firsthand
- Order products for home use
- Understand the craftsmanship

