= Platform Architecture

== Technology Stack

=== Frontend Layer
- *Framework*: Next.js 14.2.3 with App Router
- *Language*: TypeScript for type safety
- *Styling*: Tailwind CSS with custom Bonu brand colors
  - Cream: `#FDF8F3`
  - Terracotta: `#C4704A`
  - Espresso: `#3D2314`
  - Gold: `#D4A853`
- *UI Components*: shadcn/ui component library
- *State Management*: Zustand (cart management)

=== Backend Infrastructure
- *Database*: Self-hosted PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- *Authentication*: NextAuth.js with Prisma adapter
- *Storage*: Cloudflare R2 (S3-compatible) for images and workshop materials
- *Email*: Resend for transactional and marketing emails
- *Payments*: Stripe integration for workshop bookings and products

=== Deployment
- *Hosting*: DigitalOcean VPS (self-hosted)
- *Web Server*: Nginx with SSL (Let's Encrypt)
- *Containerization*: Docker Compose
- *CI/CD*: GitHub Actions for automated deployments

== New Features for Playground Model

=== Workshop Booking System

*Individual Workshop Registration*:
- Browse available workshops by topic/date
- One-click registration at £20
- Stripe payment integration
- Automatic confirmation email
- Calendar invite (Google Calendar sync)

*Workshop Administration*:
- Create workshops with topic, date, capacity
- Manage registrations and attendance
- Send reminders (24h and 1h before)
- Share materials and recordings
- Collect feedback

=== WhatsApp Community Integration

*Automated Invitation System*:
