- Generates unique invitation link
- Tracks community growth
- Segments by interests

*Content Management*:
- Schedule posts to community
- Share workshop announcements
- Poll members for topic interests
- Share quick tips and recipes

=== Analytics Dashboard

*Workshop Metrics*:
- Registration conversion rates
- Attendance rates
- Revenue per workshop topic
- Popular topics identification
- Customer acquisition cost

*Customer Insights*:
- Journey tracking (free → trial → playground)
