= Revenue Model & Projections

== Revenue Streams

*1. Workshop Revenue* \
Free workshops: £0 (marketing investment) \
Trial workshops: £15-20 × attendees \
Playground workshops: £20 × attendees

*2. Product Sales* \
Bánh mì: £9/loaf (buy 10 get 1 free) \
Beef balls: £15/500g \
Other products: Variable

*3. Private Consultations* \
1-on-1 sessions: £50-100 per 45 minutes \
Business coaching packages: £500+ (future)

== Monthly Projections (Conservative)

=== Month 1-3: Building Foundation

*Free Workshops*: \
- 2 per month × 20 attendees = 40 people
- WhatsApp community: 40 members
- Revenue: £0 (investment phase)

*Trial Workshops*: \
- 2 per month × 10 attendees × £20 = £400/month

*Playground Workshops*: \
- 4 per month × 8 attendees × £20 = £640/month

*Product Sales*: \
- 50 loaves bánh mì × £9 = £450/month
- Other products: £200/month

*Total Monthly Revenue*: ~£1,700

=== Month 4-6: Growth Phase

*Free Workshops*: \
- 2 per month × 30 attendees = 60 people
- WhatsApp community: 150+ members

*Trial + Playground*: \
- 6-8 workshops/month × 12 avg attendees × £20 = £1,440-1,920/month

*Product Sales*: \
- 100 loaves + other products = £1,200/month

*Total Monthly Revenue*: ~£3,000-3,500

=== Month 7-12: Established Phase

*Workshops*: \
- 10-12 workshops/month × 15 avg attendees × £20 = £3,000-3,600/month

*Product Sales*: \
- 150+ loaves + expanding product line = £2,000+/month

*Private Consultations*: \
- 4-6 sessions/month × £75 avg = £300-450/month

*Total Monthly Revenue*: ~£5,500-6,500/month

== Cost Structure

*Fixed Costs*:
- VPS hosting: £20/month
- Email service (Resend): £20/month
- Stripe fees: 2.9% + 30p per transaction
- Domain & SSL: £1/month (annual)
- Workshop platform (Zoom): £15/month

*Variable Costs*:
- Ingredients for product orders: ~40% of product revenue
- Guest expert fees: £50-100 per workshop (optional)
- Marketing: £100-200/month

*Total Monthly Costs*: ~£500-800 (excluding product costs)

*Net Monthly Profit* (Month 7-12): ~£3,000-4,000

